movies.title: Sleepy Eyes of Death: Castle Menagerie
movies.title_english: Sleepy Eyes of Death: Castle Menagerie
movies.title_long: Sleepy Eyes of Death: Castle Menagerie (1969)
movies.summary: Just when you think Kyoshiro's life can't get any stranger, someone starts running around raping and murdering, and leaving notes proudly proclaiming that he did it. Tracking down the real culprit willtake him along a twisted trail that involves the Shogun's harem, hidden christians, and positively pregnant politics.

movies.title: Breathless
movies.summary: Jesse has to get out of Las Vegas quickly, and steals a car to drive to L.A. On the way he shoots a police man. When he makes it to L.A. he stays with Monica, a girl he has only known for a few days. As the film progresses, the police get closer to him, and the crimes escalate.

movies.title: Farscape: The Peacekeeper Wars
movies.summary: When a full-scale war is engaged by the evil Scarran Empire, the Peacekeeper Alliance has but one hope: reassemble human astronaut John Crichton, once sucked into the Peacekeeper galaxy through a wormhole. Crichton's task: Get the entire Peacekeeper race to safety before the last war of an era brings and end to the universe.
